setfacl RBAC Lab (SOC Analyst Training)

Objective
Use `setfacl` to enforce RBAC, simulate access violations, and validate with logs and packet traces.

Tools
- Linux (Ubuntu 22.04)
- ACL (`setfacl`, `getfacl`)
- tcpdump + Wireshark

Scenarios
- RBAC enforcement
- Unauthorized access detection
- File exfiltration trace

Validation
- `getfacl` output
- Access denied logs
- Wireshark packet trace
